            <Icon class="w-6 sm:w-8 lg:w-10 xl:w-14 2xl:w-20 inline-block" name="tabler:search" />
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-secondary text-[2.7vw] sm:text-[1.3vw] font-inter -mt-[1.2vw] sm:-mt-[0.6vw]"
          >
            Previa evaluación
          </p>
